---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About the Program">
  <div class="relative bg-primary text-white py-12">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img 
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517048676732-d65bc937f952?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80"
        alt="Learning environment"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-20"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">About ELT Hospitality Class</h1>
      <p class="text-xl">Helping newcomers integrate into PEI's tourism industry</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Program Overview Section -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-2">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Program Overview</h2>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden mb-8">
          <img
            src="/image/Program Overview.jpg"
            alt="Classroom learning"
            class="w-full h-82 object-cover"
          />
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="mb-4 justify" style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.3em;">The Employment Language Training (ELT) Hospitality Program provides new immigrants to Canada (Levels 4+ with permanent resident status or Ukrainians under the CUAET pathway) with the opportunity to combine learning English and learning essential skills to help integrate them into the Prince Edward Island Tourism workplace. Classes will be held from September 2025 to June 2026 at Holland College Belmont Centre in Charlottetown.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Program Objectives Section -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Program Objectives</h3>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary mb-3">Language & Communication</h4>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                <li>Enhanced English proficiency in all four CLB areas:
                  <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4">
                    <li>Reading</li>
                    <li>Writing</li>
                    <li>Listening</li>
                    <li>Speaking</li>
                  </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Excellent customer service skills</li>
                <li>Improved communication abilities</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary mb-3">Practical Experience</h4>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                <li>PEI tourism knowledge and tour guiding</li>
                <li>Hands-on restaurant training</li>
                <li>Customer service practice in New-to-You Shop</li>
                <li>Two-week job shadow opportunity</li>
                <li>School lunch program participation</li>
                <li>Tourism event planning experience</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Certifications & Training Section -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Certifications & Training</h3>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary mb-3">Industry Certifications</h4>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                <li>EMERIT National Tourism Skills</li>
                <li>PEI Best Service Training Program</li>
                <li>Food Safety Certification</li>
                <li>WHMIS Certification</li>
                <li>Standard First Aid and CPR/AED Training Level C</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary mb-3">Additional Training</h4>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                <li>Employment Standards Workshop</li>
                <li>Human Rights Training</li>
                <li>Resume and Cover Letter Writing</li>
                <li>Restaurant Serving Skills</li>
                <li>Bus Familiarization Tour of P.E.I.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column - Instructor & Schedule -->
      <div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg mb-8">
          <div class="text-center mb-6">
            <img
              src="/image/Beverley.jpg"
              alt="Beverley Fullerton Lewis"
              class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full object-cover mx-auto mb-4"
            />
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Beverley Fullerton Lewis</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Language Training Instructor</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="prose max-w-none text-gray-700">
            <p class="mb-4 justify">As an Instructor in Language Training within Holland College's Language Instruction for Newcomers to Canada (LINC) program, Beverley Fullerton Lewis brings expertise to the Employment Language Training (ELT) Hospitality program.</p>
            <p class="mb-4 justify">Her role involves teaching specialized courses aimed at enhancing English proficiency for newcomers pursuing careers in the hospitality industry.</p>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg mt-6">
              <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Contact Information</h4>
              <p>Email: <a href="mailto:BFullertonLewis@hollandcollege.com" class="text-primary hover:text-secondary">BFullertonLewis@hollandcollege.com</a></p>
              <p>Phone: <a href="tel:19026287014" class="text-primary hover:text-secondary">(902) 628-7014</a></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-100 p-8 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Program Schedule</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
              </svg>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">Duration</h4>
                <p>September to June</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">Class Hours</h4>
                <p>Monday to Friday</p>
                <p>25 hours per week</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
              </svg>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">Location</h4>
                <p>Holland College's Belmont Centre</p>
                <p>Charlottetown, Prince Edward Island</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
.justify {
  text-align: justify;
}
</style>